            "body": "> Saying that \\\"this is just how `:mksession` works\\\" is more or less fine, but I'd expect native solution to be more polished.\n\nI think we can start with an implementation that has these minor issues, and then iterate from there (especially because that involves improving sessions in general, not just for `:restart`).",
